  h3 Square Icon Buttons

  p.
    #[code .btn--icon] &mdash; makes square buttons when only a single character, pictogram or (#[a(href="http://fontawesome.io/icons/") Font Awesome]) icon is present within the button.

  p
    button.btn.btn--success.btn--icon
      i.fa.fa-arrow-right

    button.btn.btn--secondary.btn--icon
      i.fa.fa-folder-open-o

    button.btn.btn--primary.btn--icon
